Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 04 of Hip MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Alignment' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Regular joint position' radio button is enabled
And 'Pathology' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Pathology' radio button
Then 'Right' checkbox is enabled
And 'Left' checkbox is enabled
And 'Centered' radio button is enabled
And 'Decentered' radio button is enabled
And 'Dislocated' radio button is enabled

And 'Dysplasia'checkbox is enabled
And 'Epiphysiolysis' checkbox is enabled


When I select 'Dysplasia' checkbox
Then 'Flattened' checkbox is enabled
And 'Insufficiency' radio button is enabled
And 'Enlarged' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Epiphysiolysis' checkbox
Then 'Epiphyseal bone marrow edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Enlarged epiphyseal plate' checkbox is enabled
And 'Irregular epiphyseal plate' checkbox is enabled
And 'Crushed physis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Dislocated femoral head' checkbox is enabled
